## Description {#details}

Root entry.

ASSUMPTION: 3 bits are used to store <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf-linker/parallel/dependencytracker/#acb3226f07be871308b3ebc1fe2e22ad8">LiveRootWorklistActionTy</a> value. Thus <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf-linker/parallel/dependencytracker/#acb3226f07be871308b3ebc1fe2e22ad8">LiveRootWorklistActionTy</a> should have no more eight elements. Pointer traits for <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarf-linker/parallel/compileunit">CompileUnit</a>.
